                        <string>&lt;html&gt;&lt;head/&gt;&lt;body&gt;&lt;h4 style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt; font-weight:700;&quot;&gt;Função: Buscar NCM&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt;&quot;&gt;Essa função permite ao usuário buscar um NCM específico digitado por ele. A tabela será atualizada para mostrar apenas os resultados que correspondem ao NCM digitado.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt; font-weight:700;&quot;&gt;Passos:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt;&quot;&gt;1: Digite o NCM desejado no campo de busca.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt;&quot;&gt;2: Clique no botão &amp;quot;Buscar NCM&amp;quot;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt;&quot;&gt;3: A tabela será atualizada para mostrar os resultados que correspondem ao NCM digitado.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
                       </property>
                       <property name="margin">
                        <number>1</number>
                       </property>
                      </widget>
                     </item>
                    </layout>
                   </widget>
                   <widget class="QWidget" name="page_ncm_invalido">
                    <layout class="QGridLayout" name="gridLayout_18">
                     <item row="0" column="0">
                      <widget class="QLabel" name="label">
                       <property name="text">
                        <string>&lt;html&gt;&lt;head/&gt;&lt;body&gt;&lt;h4 style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt; font-weight:700;&quot;&gt;Função: NCM Inválido&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt;&quot;&gt;Essa função busca por todos os NCMs que estão vencidos na tabela. Isso é útil para identificar rapidamente itens que precisam de atualização.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt; font-weight:700;&quot;&gt;Passos:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt;&quot;&gt;1: Clique no botão &amp;quot;NCM Inválido&amp;quot;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt;&quot;&gt;2: A tabela será atualizada para mostrar todos os NCMs que estão vencidos.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
                       </property>
                       <property name="textFormat">
                        <enum>Qt::TextFormat::AutoText</enum>
                       </property>
                      </widget>
                     </item>
                    </layout>
                   </widget>
                   <widget class="QWidget" name="page_tudo_que_contem">
                    <layout class="QGridLayout" name="gridLayout_19">
                     <item row="0" column="0">
                      <widget class="QLabel" name="label_5">
                       <property name="text">
                        <string>&lt;html&gt;&lt;head/&gt;&lt;body&gt;&lt;h4 style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt; font-weight:700;&quot;&gt;Função: Tudo que Contém&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt;&quot;&gt;Essa função permite ao usuário fazer uma busca na tabela para encontrar itens que contenham o texto digitado ou itens similares.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt; font-weight:700;&quot;&gt;Passos:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt;&quot;&gt;1: Digite o texto desejado no campo de busca.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt;&quot;&gt;2: Clique no botão &amp;quot;Tudo que Contém&amp;quot;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt;&quot;&gt;3: A tabela será atualizada para mostrar os resultados que contêm o texto digitado ou itens similares.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
                       </property>
                      </widget>
                     </item>
                    </layout>
                   </widget>
                   <widget class="QWidget" name="page">
                    <layout class="QGridLayout" name="gridLayout_26">
                     <item row="0" column="0">
                      <widget class="QPlainTextEdit" name="txt_analise_inteligente_output"/>
                     </item>
                    </layout>
                   </widget>
                   <widget class="QWidget" name="page_op_busca_dados_duplicados">
                    <layout class="QGridLayout" name="gridLayout_20">
                     <item row="0" column="0">
                      <widget class="QLabel" name="label_6">
                       <property name="text">
                        <string>&lt;html&gt;&lt;head/&gt;&lt;body&gt;&lt;h4 align=&quot;justify&quot; style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt; font-weight:700;&quot;&gt;Função: Dados Duplicados&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt;&quot;&gt;Essa função atualiza a tabela para marcar todas as linhas que são iguais, levando em conta colunas como descrição, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt;&quot;&gt;código interno, código de barras, etc. As linhas duplicadasserão destacadas em vermelho para facilitar a identificação.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt; font-weight:700;&quot;&gt;Passos:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt;&quot;&gt;1: Clique no botão &amp;quot;Dados Duplicados&amp;quot;. 2: A tabela será atualizada e todas as linhas &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p align=&quot;justify&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt;&quot;&gt;duplicadas serão destacadas em vermelho.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
                       </property>
                      </widget>
                     </item>
                    </layout>
                   </widget>
                  </widget>
                 </item>
                </layout>
               </widget>
