                   <widget class="QWidget" name="page_substituir_ncm">
                    <layout class="QGridLayout" name="gridLayout_21">
                     <item row="0" column="0">
                      <widget class="QLabel" name="label_7">
                       <property name="text">
                        <string>&lt;html&gt;&lt;head/&gt;&lt;body&gt;&lt;h4 style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt; font-weight:700;&quot;&gt;Função: Substituir NCM&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt;&quot;&gt;Essa função verifica o NCM digitado no primeiro campo e substitui o NCM encontrado na tabela por outro digitado no segundo campo.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt; font-weight:700;&quot;&gt;Passos:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt; font-weight:700;&quot;&gt;1&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt;&quot;&gt;: Digite o NCM a ser substituído no primeiro campo. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt; font-weight:700;&quot;&gt;2:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt;&quot;&gt; Digite o novo NCM no segundo campo.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt; font-weight:700;&quot;&gt;3:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt;&quot;&gt; Clique no botão &amp;quot;Substituir NCM&amp;quot;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt; font-weight:700;&quot;&gt; 4:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt;&quot;&gt; A tabela será atualizada com as substituições.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
                       </property>
                      </widget>
                     </item>
                    </layout>
                   </widget>
                   <widget class="QWidget" name="page_colunaA_colunaB_recebe">
                    <layout class="QGridLayout" name="gridLayout_22">
                     <item row="0" column="0">
                      <widget class="QLabel" name="label_8">
                       <property name="text">
                        <string>&lt;html&gt;&lt;head/&gt;&lt;body&gt;&lt;h4 style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:7pt; font-weight:700;&quot;&gt;Função: Se Coluna A contém, Coluna B recebe&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt;&quot;&gt;Essa função verifica se a coluna selecionada no ComboBox 1 contém o dado digitado e, se sim, substitui os valores na &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt;&quot;&gt;coluna selecionada no ComboBox 2.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt; font-weight:700;&quot;&gt;1: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt;&quot;&gt;Selecione a coluna a ser verificada no ComboBox 1. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt; font-weight:700;&quot;&gt;2: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt;&quot;&gt;Digite o dado a ser verificado no primeiro campo. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt; font-weight:700;&quot;&gt;3: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt;&quot;&gt;Selecione a coluna a ser alterada no ComboBox 2. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt; font-weight:700;&quot;&gt;4: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt;&quot;&gt;Digite o novo valor no segundo campo.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt; font-weight:700;&quot;&gt;5: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt;&quot;&gt;Clique no botão &amp;quot;Se Coluna A contém, Coluna B recebe&amp;quot;. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt; font-weight:700;&quot;&gt;6: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt;&quot;&gt;A tabela será atualizada com as alterações.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
                       </property>
                      </widget>
                     </item>
                    </layout>
                   </widget>
                   <widget class="QWidget" name="page_filtrar_coluna_linhas_contem">
                    <layout class="QGridLayout" name="gridLayout_23">
                     <item row="0" column="0">
                      <widget class="QLabel" name="label_9">
                       <property name="text">
                        <string>&lt;html&gt;&lt;head/&gt;&lt;body&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:7pt; font-weight:700;&quot;&gt;Função: Filtrar por Coluna e Copiar Todas as Linhas que Contenham&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt;&quot;&gt;Essa função filtra os dados da tabela com base na coluna e no texto digitados, &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt;&quot;&gt;e permite ao usuário salvar o resultado em CSV.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt; font-weight:700;&quot;&gt;1: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt;&quot;&gt;Selecione a coluna a ser filtrada no ComboBox 1. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt; font-weight:700;&quot;&gt;2: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt;&quot;&gt;Digite o texto a ser filtrado no primeiro campo.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt; font-weight:700;&quot;&gt;3: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt;&quot;&gt;Selecione a coluna a ser alterada no ComboBox 2. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt; font-weight:700;&quot;&gt;4: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt;&quot;&gt;Digite o novo valor no segundo campo.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt; font-weight:700;&quot;&gt;5: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt;&quot;&gt;Clique no botão &amp;quot;Filtrar por Coluna e Copiar Todas as Linhas que Contenham&amp;quot;.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt; font-weight:700;&quot;&gt;6: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt;&quot;&gt;A tabela será atualizada com os dados filtrados, e você pode salvar o resultado em CSV.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
                       </property>
                      </widget>
                     </item>
                    </layout>
                   </widget>
                   <widget class="QWidget" name="page_extrair_duplicados">
                    <layout class="QGridLayout" name="gridLayout_24">
                     <item row="0" column="0">
                      <widget class="QLabel" name="label_10">
                       <property name="text">
                        <string>&lt;html&gt;&lt;head/&gt;&lt;body&gt;&lt;h4 style=&quot; margin-top:12px; margin-bottom:12px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt; font-weight:700;&quot;&gt;Função: Extrair Dados Duplicados da Tabela&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt;&quot;&gt;Essa funcionalidade verifica todas as linhas com dados iguais, levando em consideração colunas como descrição e código, marca esses dados em vermelho e permite ao usuário extrair os dados repetidos para uma nova tabela.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt; font-weight:700;&quot;&gt;Passos:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt; font-weight:700;&quot;&gt;1: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt;&quot;&gt;Clique no botão &amp;quot;Extrair Dados Duplicados&amp;quot;. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt; font-weight:700;&quot;&gt;2 &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt;&quot;&gt;A tabela será atualizada com as linhas duplicadas marcadas em vermelho.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt; font-weight:700;&quot;&gt;3: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt;&quot;&gt;Clique no botão &amp;quot;Extrair e Salvar&amp;quot;. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt; font-weight:700;&quot;&gt;4: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt;&quot;&gt;Os dados duplicados serão salvos em uma nova tabela, permitindo um &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot; font-size:6pt;&quot;&gt;processamento mais fácil.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</string>
                       </property>
                      </widget>
                     </item>
                    </layout>
                   </widget>
                  </widget>
                 </item>
                </layout>
               </widget>
              </item>
             </layout>
            </widget>
           </widget>
          </item>
         </layout>
        </widget>
       </item>
